{"type": "article", "id": 63841, "title": "塔可钟将开家同名主题精品酒店，小罗伯特唐尼代言一加手机 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-05-17T05:54:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6232, "name": "芭蕾舞"}, {"id": 667, "name": "酒店"}, {"id": 8964, "name": "塔可钟"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190517123244xgRiGsmZUVLDTdWw.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"0QHm\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/3871046669/4372598345453845\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>小罗伯特唐尼成为一加手机品牌推广大使。</b></a>昨天一加 7/7 Pro 的发布会上品牌宣布了代言消息，小罗伯特唐尼还为广告片撰写了脚本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123309KxmsnGfJhjIpWXCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"2fcs\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2793293964/4372853598095315\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>小猪短租宣布邓伦成为品牌代言人，</b></a>之前代言人是黄子韬。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123325R6BKOmniYJIf0qSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"rRFI\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1835097604/4372863974732789\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐官方微博今天发布了一张彩虹色便利店冷柜照片。</b></a>冷柜排列了 6 种不同颜色的产品，正好构成彩虹色，来纪念 5 月 17 日“国际不再恐同日 ”。文案“不怕不同，到处彩虹”与今日主题和便利店氛围都很呼应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123342Z12jGCB3LIKVg7Sk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Vg8m\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/creative-works/project/design-army-hong-kong-ballet-hong-kong-ballets-40th-anniversary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>香港芭蕾舞团发布成立 40 周年短片创意很不错。</b></a>片中演员们用芭蕾舞展示了香港的传统文化和流行现象，拍摄地选择了香港地标比如维港、传统的早茶餐厅。同时发布的海报也是传统和现代的结合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0871bo8ifh\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123356Gt15zXvVEjwfqTYu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123357xsGSWecb4UmNIKdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123357nX5T6hu3b2EJfroL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123358O0ykZunmrdLwe8WK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123358ZjdDG4HxY5vhuEbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123359cJv5yFIe8kKVsQNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123359AOzHmqMgaxEonedi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.564062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123358XzjDGnaMkx3SvhmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"xL1C\"><a href=\"http:// https://lbbonline.com/news/these-beautiful-prints-bring-famous-penguin-novels-to-life/?mc_cid=00f095e96f&amp;mc_eid=91f18d8115\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>企鹅出版品牌活动 “Lose yourself in a book” 描绘了著名小说中的场景。</b></a>这些精美的印刷品包括小说《德古拉》、《查理和巧克力工厂》和《了不起的盖茨比》，用复杂的绘画细节展示了小说情节。创意代理商是 Cheil Worldwide 北京和 Cheil Worldwide 香港。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123536xMR2915JHlNcwgGv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123536W8QYrjs2HaE3oqCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123537Zv0d3PWM1Abpjuqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123537PSVKUvHCJltBNRFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123538ne6EDlTB2Pbx0Far.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645161\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123537WP0FwL4REM62uUZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"hEaY\"><a href=\"https://www.tacobell.com/the-bell-hotel?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=E5-Bell-Hotel&amp;utm_content=organic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Taco Bell 今年夏天将限时开放一家 “The Bell” 精品酒店。</b></a>品牌介绍从酒店客房、早餐甚至是鸡尾酒都会融入 Taco Bell 元素。酒店位于加州棕榈泉，将于 6 月份开放预订。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190517123557Hi4FjEtV7OAulUTL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l08719xsba2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"CXJV\"><a href=\"http://allowFullScreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; https://m.weibo.cn/3705837112/4371804108012000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>领英发布了支短片探讨 “找准位置有多重要”。</b></a>故事由一个人找到自己合适的工作开启，连锁反应出一系列奇幻职业成绩。领英同时联动营销号和推广这次活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l08719xsba2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"vZB0\"><a href=\"http://Hong Kong Ballet is celebrating its 40th anniversary by using its dancers to showcase ballet and pop culture around various landmarks in Hong Kong.  Shot at places like basketball courts, Victoria Harbor, and a traditional banquet hall, the campaign uses dancers to show off martial arts, fashion and even Chinese grandmas to dance against the backdrop of Ravel’s Boléro orchestral blend of hip hop, classical and heritage.  Sheer beauty, gravity-defying movement and humor collide with cheeky Chinese grannies mimicking dancers, a traditional dragon with brightly colorful legs on point; and a happy emoji ending. Defiantly unconventional, this campaign defines Hong Kong Ballet: moving forward, never standing still.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>沃尔玛发布 2019 年第一季度财报，营收增长 1%，美国同店销售增长 3.4%。</b></a></p><p line=\"yKU0\">沃尔玛美国 3.4% 的同店销售增长是 9 年来最高，主要受到电商、复活节购物季推动。但沃尔玛还在努力与亚马逊竞争，本周宣布开始推出一日达配送服务，同时考虑对部分中国进口商品加价。UBS 分析师 Michael Lasser 称，沃尔玛大约 有26% 的商品进口自中国，相比例如塔吉特的 34% 的比例较低。</p><p line=\"6LrZ\"><a href=\"https://36kr.com/newsflashes/167648\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>喜茶北京首家热麦店在五棵松华熙 LIVE 开业。</b></a>这次店内除了茶饮和现场制作的软欧包之外，还推出多款北京特色产品。比如和餐饮品牌姥姥家联名推出的懒龙包、京酱肉丝包，以及融合二锅头和茶饮的“赭韵”“京桂”饮品等。</p><p line=\"SBaV\"><a href=\"https://fashionunited.uk/news/business/looking-to-accelerate-international-expansion-24-sevres-changes-its-name-to-24s/2019051643210\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团旗下电商网站 24 Sèvres 正式更名为 24S，</b></a>来加快电商在美国和亚洲等海外市场的发展，认为新名称更容易在国际范围内传播。网站自 2017 年推出后，收到了 100 多个国家和地区的订单，接下来会专注有巨大潜力的市场。</p><p line=\"SBaV\" class=\"\">题图来自：Taco Bell</p>"}